column2: SELECT TOP # photospec.ra, photospec.dec, photospec.z, photospec.cx, photospec.cy, photospec.cz, zoo.spiral, zoo.elliptical, zoo.uncertain, photospec.petroMag_r, pz.absMagR FROM SpecPhotoAll AS photospec JOIN zooSpec AS zoo ON zoo.objid = photospec.objid JOIN photoz AS pz ON pz.objid = photospec.objid WHERE photospec.ra BETWEEN # AND # AND photospec.dec BETWEEN # AND # AND photospec.z BETWEEN # AND # AND photospec.zWarning = # AND photospec.petroMag_r < # AND photospec.type = # AND zoo.spiral = # OR zoo.elliptical = # AND pz.absMagR < #
